  "original_title": "6 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 1486 \u0bb5\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0bb5\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1 \u0bb5\u0bc6\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bc7\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba9\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "1486 doctors left the country in 6 months",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "1486 doctors have left the country in the first 6 months of this year alone.",
        "According to the data of Sri Lanka Medical Council, this year 138 doctors left the country in January, 172 doctors in February, 198 doctors in March, 214 doctors in April, 315 doctors in May and 449 doctors in June.",
        "It is known that they have left the country after obtaining the certificate from the Medical Council of Sri Lanka."
      ],
